text: "Sherry" is a 1962 song by The Four Seasons. It is the second single from their debut studio album Sherry & 11 Others. It went to number 1 in Canada, New Zealand and the United States, number 8 in the United Kingdom and number 3 in Australia. ==References== Category:1962 songs Category:The Four Seasons (band) songs Category:Pop rock songs
title: Sherry (song)
